<P>
MANILA, June 22 (Xinhua) -- Filipino billiards sensation Efren
Reyes vowed Thursday to do his best to retain his title as he
leads three other top Philippine cue artists in the 2000 World
Professional Pool Championship slated on July 1-11 in Cardiff,
Britain.
