<HEADLINE> Xi'an Launches Software Development Platform </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Xi'an, June 22 (Xinhua) -- The transnational IT giant IBM and
Xi'an Times Information Industry Group (XTIIG) today jointly
launched a software development platform in this capital of
northwest China's Shaanxi Province, offering technological
services for all software enterprises.
</P>
