<HEADLINE> Forum To Open to Boost Commercialization of IT results </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The forum aims to foster partnership between IT researchers and
the business sector, enabling IT researchers, industrialists and
investment professionals to meet and share views and experience
over the commercialization of IT research results.
</P>
<P>
It provides an opportunity for academics to transform their IT
research results into applications with the necessary support from
the industry.
</P>
