population and education of the younger generation, she said.
Efforts should be made to improve the quality of all Chinese women,
she noted.
</P>
<P>
Peng attacked those who infringe on the legal rights and
interests of women such as gender discrimination in employment,
labor protection for women workers, and family violence.
</P>
<P>
The Federation must improve laws, regulations and policies
concerning women's affairs, Peng said.
</P>
<P>
