Wednesday on the charges of involving in Bali Bank corruption
scandal.
</P>
<P>
Marzuki also said if corruption evidences are found, other
people who were involved in the Bali scandal will also be detained.
</P>
<P>
The Bali scandal revolves around Bank Indonesia's reimbursement
of 904 billion rupiah (129 million U.S. dollars)in defaulted loans
to other banks. Some 546 billion rupiah (78 million U.S. dollars)
of the money was then paid to PT Era Giat Prima for helping Bali
Bank recoup the money. There is suspicion that a large portion of
the money went to the then ruling party of Golkar to run for the
presidential renomination bid of BJ. Habibie.
</P>
<P>
Local reports said, some former ministers including former head
of the Supreme Advisory Council Arnold A. Baramuli, a close friend
of former president BJ. Habibie, were involved in the Bali scandal.
</P>
