Mohammad Khatami on Wednesday to inform him of the official
admission of Iran into the Group-15.
</P>
<P>
Iran's membership was endorsed at the 10th summit of the group
in Cairo which concluded on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
The Egyptian Gazette:
</P>
<P>
-- Egyptian President Hosni Mubarak on Wednesday met economic
ministerial group and discussed investment, financial and banking
issues and reviewed the outcome of the G-15 summit. 
