</P>
<P>
Rachel McQuillan, Australia, bt Francesca Lubiani, Italy, 6-1,
6-7 (4-7), 6-1
</P>
<P>
Greta Arn, Germany, bt 6-Francesca Schiavone, Italy, 7-6 (7-2),
6-4
</P>
<P>
4-Giulia Casoni, Italy, bt Marion Maruska, Austria, 6-2, 7-6 (7-
3)
</P>
<P>
Angelika Bachmann, Germany, bt Heidi Farr, Britain, 6-1, 6-7 (5-
7), 6-2
